                        </layout>
                     </layoutDesc>
                  </objectDesc>
                  <handDesc>
                     <p>Line 4 is written in a second hand.  The vertical stroke in the obol sign in line 2 is longer than usual and the fraction 1/2 is indistinct, but the long diagonal stroke of the fraction 1/4 is clear.  The hedj sign in line 2 is relatively clear and the hair determinative at the end of the tax name supports reading inshn, as does the amount paid.</p>
